---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Riconoscimenti foto | Dott.ssa Annachiara Lorusso"
  description="Riconoscimenti delle immagini utilizzate nel sito."
>
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-site max-w-3xl">
      <p class="section-eyebrow mb-3">Riconoscimenti</p>
      <h1 class="font-headline text-4xl leading-tight text-secondary md:text-5xl">Crediti fotografici</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-on-surface-variant">
        Questa pagina raccoglie i crediti delle immagini utilizzate nel sito, con link alle fonti originali.
      </p>

      <ul class="mt-10 space-y-4">
        <li class="card-soft-elevated rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/35 p-4">
          <p class="font-semibold text-on-surface">home-aree.jpg</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">
            Foto di Sena Kaleli su Pexels:
            <a
              href="https://www.pexels.com/it-it/foto/29697155/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
              class="text-secondary underline decoration-secondary/50 underline-offset-4 hover:text-tertiary"
            >
              https://www.pexels.com/it-it/foto/29697155/
            </a>
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="card-soft-elevated rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/35 p-4">
          <p class="font-semibold text-on-surface">servizi.jpg</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">
            Foto di Pixabay su Pexels:
            <a
              href="https://www.pexels.com/it-it/foto/persona-che-scrive-sul-taccuino-rosso-261735/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
              class="text-secondary underline decoration-secondary/50 underline-offset-4 hover:text-tertiary"
            >
              https://www.pexels.com/it-it/foto/persona-che-scrive-sul-taccuino-rosso-261735/
            </a>
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="card-soft-elevated rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/35 p-4">
          <p class="font-semibold text-on-surface">aree-intervento-1.jpg</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">
            Foto di Pixabay su Pexels:
            <a
              href="https://www.pexels.com/it-it/foto/cairn-stones-e-specchio-d-acqua-in-lontananza-235990/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
              class="text-secondary underline decoration-secondary/50 underline-offset-4 hover:text-tertiary"
            >
              https://www.pexels.com/it-it/foto/cairn-stones-e-specchio-d-acqua-in-lontananza-235990/
            </a>
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="card-soft-elevated rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/35 p-4">
          <p class="font-semibold text-on-surface">aree-intervento-2.jpg</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">
            Foto di Dawafenjo Gurung su Pexels:
            <a
              href="https://www.pexels.com/it-it/foto/impianto-pianta-piantine-fotografia-di-piante-4118322/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer"
              class="text-secondary underline decoration-secondary/50 underline-offset-4 hover:text-tertiary"
            >
              https://www.pexels.com/it-it/foto/impianto-pianta-piantine-fotografia-di-piante-4118322/
            </a>
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="card-soft-elevated rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/35 p-4">
          <p class="font-semibold text-on-surface">portrait.jpeg</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-on-surface-variant">
            Ritratto professionale fornito direttamente dalla cliente.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
